column4: <content>[1 blad] 6a. Landschaft mit Versuchung St. Antonius. Jedlicka, citaat p. 540; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Treatment of the soil very different from P.B.I: long broad brush strokes in contrast to P.B.'s spotted ground - also the rocks, the plants different in character. Lack of precision of form in figures. Foliage also different. Not certain whether Jan B. But who else?'</content>
<documentation.title>Pieter Bruegel : der Maler in seiner Zeit</documentation.title>
